label: Negligible
comment: This threat or asset behaviour has no significant direct impact on business functionality or efficiency.

label: Very Low
comment: This threat or asset behaviour causes a small loss of business functionality or efficiency.

label: Low
comment: This threat or asset behaviour causes a moderate loss of business functionality or efficiency.

label: Medium
comment: This threat or asset behaviour causes a serious but non-fatal loss of business functionality or efficiency.

label: High
comment: This threat or asset behaviour causes a serious loss of business functionality that will be fatal if not stopped very quickly.

label: Very High
comment: This threat or asset behaviour is fatal to key business objectives, must be prevented at all costs.
